rora，樓豬跟團冇得揀唯有搭Aurora<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/080916_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F080916_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=94073f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個餐盒靚過因航咁多嘅喂<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/081036_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F081036_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=3532437a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連埋轉機搭左10幾個鐘終於到<br />\n同總理同一日到所以成個機場都係政府機<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/081324_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F081324_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=5661fb9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲飛機可以拎去博物館展覽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/081329_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F081329_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=85b2b931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似係代表俄羅斯領土嘅起點(勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/081546_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F081546_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=6451fa24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄羅斯料理<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/081924_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F081924_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=8d4aab77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/081928_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F081928_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=b68e797d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n住宿係喺渡假村<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/082130_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F082130_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=11bb9422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/082135_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F082135_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=ef104a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/082140_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F082140_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=c0f5062a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後到埗第二日就已經開始露營。。。"},{"pid":"5b197c7425ed508d3b393aaac331289928716283","tid":778620,"uid":153878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"第3&amp;4日 Mutnovsky Volcano<br />\n<br />\n今次用嘅越野軍車<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/083512_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F083512_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=6ef15973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個景靚就點影都靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/083632_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F083632_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=3ec74de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMutnovsky火山瞭望台<br />\n<img sr